heading: 2. The 1st day of March 2022 is appointed as the day on which sections 9
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of March 2022 is appointed as the day on which sections 9 
and 10 of the Greyhound Racing Act 2019 (No. 15 of 2019) come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

23 February, 2022. 

CHARLIE MCCONALOGUE, 

Minister for Agriculture, Food and the Marine. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 25th February, 2022.
